\binom{n}{1}+2\binom{n}{2}+3\binom{n}{3}+\cdots+n\binom{n}{n}=
=n\binom{n-1}{0}+2\frac{n}{2}\binom{n-1}{1}+3\frac{n}{3}\binom{n-1}{2}+\cdots+n\binom{n-1}{n-1}=
=n\binom{n-1}{0}+n\binom{n-1}{1}+n\binom{n-1}{2}+\cdots+n\binom{n-1}{n-1}=
=n\left(\binom{n-1}{0}+\binom{n-1}{1}+\binom{n-1}{2}+\cdots+\binom{n-1}{n-1}\right)=n2^{n-1}
